title: Sauder August Hill L-Shaped Desk Review (Links in Description)
description:
Sauder August Hill L-Shaped Desk, Dover Oak Finish Review
This cost about $210, 4 hours build time. Its fiber or pressed board, features a file or storage drawer, a technology pier,  and under-desk storage. Comprehensive cable management and routing paths. Large surface area (59.1 x 58.7 x 29.2 inches) and and oak finish.

This is the first product review I've ever done. This is NOT a sponsored video.
